description: Four people have been killed in a gun attack in the Austrian capital. Here's what we know.
title: Vienna shooting: What we know about 'Islamist terror' attack
title_page: Vienna shooting: What we know about 'Islamist terror' attack - BBC News
maintext: Initially police were unsure how many attackers there were. Some witnesses spoke of two or more, and it took almost two days for police to go through thousands of hours of mobile phone footage to determine that the gunman was acting alone.
